<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">開示偈</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示剡水禪人</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<lb ed="X" n="0303a13"/><milestone unit="juan" n="18"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a01"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="018"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="18"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>無異禪師廣錄卷第十八</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a15"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a02"/><byline cb:type="editor">住博山法孫　弘瀚　彚編</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a03"/><byline cb:type="collector">首座法孫　弘裕　同集</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a04"/><p cb:type="head1" xml:id="pX72p0303a1801">開示偈<note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示劉自度居士</cb:mulu><head>示劉自度居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303a2001">沒蹤跡處莫藏身。釣盡澄江躍浪鱗。藏身之處沒蹤
<lb ed="X" n="0303a21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a07"/>跡。華亭兩岸花狼籍。迸破虗空別有天。綠楊深處草
<lb ed="X" n="0303a22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a08"/>芊芊。更須簡點家常事。跛脚驢兒在後園。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示智璘居士</cb:mulu><head>示智璘居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303a24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a10"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303a2401">眾生心佛無差別。大理不明誓不輟。一朝識得本來
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0303b" n="0303b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a11"/>人。頓悟無生方欣悅。兒女團圞古道塲。動步先須達
<lb ed="X" n="0303b02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a12"/>本鄉。父母未生前面目。著衣喫飯是家常。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示悟言禪座</cb:mulu><head>示悟言禪座</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a14"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303b0401">立志脩行須犖卓。還如美玉重雕琢。雕到玲瓏八面
<lb ed="X" n="0303b05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a15"/>時。功成始得稱無學。放下塵緣即便休。青山何事使
<lb ed="X" n="0303b06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a16"/>人愁。牧鞭收向明珠庫。放出溈山水牯牛。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示吳觀我宮諭</cb:mulu><head>示吳觀我宮諭</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239a18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303b0801">麈尾縱橫劫外春。一番拈弄一番新。油缾勘破投明
<lb ed="X" n="0303b09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b01"/>客。茶話輸他返拜人。孝滿酒顛欣逆子。劍揮巢破驗
<lb ed="X" n="0303b10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b02"/>忠臣。不辭竿盡重栽竹。喜得華亭躍浪鱗。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示蔣熈臺居士</cb:mulu><head>示蔣熈臺居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b04"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303b1201">聖道無依不揀人。入門何必斷貪嗔。月盛銀盌含秋
<lb ed="X" n="0303b13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b05"/>碧。露浸松濤帶曉雲。清淨界中纔一念。輪迴路上幾
<lb ed="X" n="0303b14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b06"/>生身。話頭頓破閻浮夢。瑞草靈苗說似君。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示湛如禪人</cb:mulu><head>示湛如禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b08"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303b1601">圓明湛湛妙無垠。如涉纖毫即是塵。大地都來銀世
<lb ed="X" n="0303b17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b09"/>界。更於何處覓金身。休云妄莫分真。祇知一馬生三
<lb ed="X" n="0303b18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b10"/>寅。匝地清風何所有。笑看鸚鵡過西秦。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示江憶州居士</cb:mulu><head>示江憶州居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303b2001">摩尼江岸若何求。直向驪龍頷下搜。喝轉迅流須勇
<lb ed="X" n="0303b21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b13"/>決。吸乾滄海任遨遊。挐雲<anchor xml:id="beg_71" type="cb-app"/><g ref="#CB05181">󱐽</g><anchor xml:id="end_71"/>浪憑雙手。倒嶽傾湫祇
<lb ed="X" n="0303b22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b14"/>一頭。眉底頓開無礙眼。光明普照四神洲。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示張興公居士</cb:mulu><head>示張興公居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303b24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b16"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303b2401">橫身宇宙沒遮攔。盡力推爺山外山。不辯金光珍燕
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0303c" n="0303c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b17"/>石。十方消殞謾追攀。脫筌網躍靈源。變化風雲頃刻
<lb ed="X" n="0303c02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0239b18"/>間。此是洞曹兼帶旨。為君款款露全斑。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示蕭若拙郡伯</cb:mulu><head>示蕭若拙郡伯</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a02"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303c0401">不逐形儀觀實相。玄機獨露面門餘。忘言寶藏流千
<lb ed="X" n="0303c05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a03"/>古。爍夢真光徹太虗。石女繡空花有果。木人敲火燄
<lb ed="X" n="0303c06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a04"/>生魚。本源妙粹離非即。待客迎賓體自如。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a05"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303c0701">待客迎賓體自如。何勞緣木復求魚。靈心洞燭山河
<lb ed="X" n="0303c08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a06"/>影。慧眼旋觀物象虗。插草欣投當指地。拈花偏向笑
<lb ed="X" n="0303c09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a07"/>顏餘。而今<g ref="#CB05338">𠢐</g>破娘生面。眉目依然不是渠。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示黃玄石居士</cb:mulu><head>示黃玄石居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303c1101">出塵無染毒龍腥。世道鴻毛一樣輕。幻化塲中誰是
<lb ed="X" n="0303c12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a10"/>我。電光影裏孰為情。楞嚴讀罷知空殞。寶所登時愛
<lb ed="X" n="0303c13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a11"/>路平。自古圓通門大啟。想君足下紫雲生。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈契玄上座</cb:mulu><head>贈契玄上座</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a13"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303c1501">圓契拈花意。重研寶鏡玄。弘施彰正令。妙挾驗真傳。
<lb ed="X" n="0303c16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a14"/>峭壁深春翠。靈花帶晚煙。當軒持萬象。印破水中天。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示孤月禪人</cb:mulu><head>示孤月禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a16"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303c1801">講席都遊遍。來參沒味禪。鋤雲栽紫芋。引水種青蓮。
<lb ed="X" n="0303c19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a17"/><g ref="#CB15035">䆳</g>谷嵐浮樹。乾柴火少煙。松風與夜月。相向不須錢。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示金燦宇居士</cb:mulu><head>示金燦宇居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b01"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303c2101">日用事無別。避喧轉覺難。飯餘歌晝永。燭盡笑更殘。
<lb ed="X" n="0303c22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b02"/>一切但仍舊。萬般都是閒。纔生分別想。知隔幾重山。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示魁杓居士二</cb:mulu><head>示魁杓居士二</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0303c24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b04"/><p xml:id="pX72p0303c2401">信心功德聚。凡聖莫岐分。放出唯三要。收來祇一塵。
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0304a" n="0304a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b05"/>不從他變態。毋用自紛紜。識得衣中寶。何愁徹骨貧。
<lb ed="X" n="0304a02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b06"/>信心功德聚。真箇火中蓮。曠劫元無異。今生幸有緣。
<lb ed="X" n="0304a03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b07"/>揭開塵界網。印破水中天。最喜金剛寶。光明照大千。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示龔可濟居士</cb:mulu><head>示龔可濟居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304a0501">苦海何為檝。誠心可濟然。慈風清性水。慧日麗中天。
<lb ed="X" n="0304a06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b10"/>華藏嚴身相。靈山在目前。須知塵界裏。烈火綻青蓮。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示李虗雲居士</cb:mulu><head>示李虗雲居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304a0801">話頭一句如弦直。岸柳巖花露法身。幾向綠楊深處
<lb ed="X" n="0304a09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b13"/>看。端然一點不沾塵。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示劉自度居士</cb:mulu><head>示劉自度居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304a1101">話頭一句如弦直。多少行人步不前。趨入便須著眼
<lb ed="X" n="0304a12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b16"/>看。香雲深處徹重玄。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示李何事居士</cb:mulu><head>示李何事居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0240b18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304a1401">話頭一句如弦直。釣盡長江獲赤鱗。步下葛藤都絆
<lb ed="X" n="0304a15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a01"/>斷。超然無累逐時新。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示王元淳居士</cb:mulu><head>示王元淳居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304a1701">話頭一句如弦直。耀日精金覿面看。行過水晶宮殿
<lb ed="X" n="0304a18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a04"/>去。門前尚有玉欄干。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示卓無量居士</cb:mulu><head>示卓無量居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304a2001">話頭一句如弦直。珠若澄兮水自清。徹見本來真面
<lb ed="X" n="0304a21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a07"/>目。方知人我不關情。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示陳旻昭居士</cb:mulu><head>示陳旻昭居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304a23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304a2301">話頭一句如弦直。香象奔波失却威。截斷狂瀾觀自
<lb ed="X" n="0304a24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a10"/>在。旃檀林裏鳳凰飛。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0304b" n="0304b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示張興公居士</cb:mulu><head>示張興公居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304b0201">話波一句如弦直。滴水高興幾丈波。出沒雲煙無限
<lb ed="X" n="0304b03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a13"/>量。空花陽<g ref="#CB08504">𦦨</g>奈渠何。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示楊仲宜居士</cb:mulu><head>示楊仲宜居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304b0501">話頭一句如弦直。行遍閻浮不識人。拄杖頭邊親磕
<lb ed="X" n="0304b06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a16"/>著。深知痛癢是關津。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示顧長卿居士</cb:mulu><head>示顧長卿居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241a18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304b0801">話頭一句如弦直。甘露還從天上來。八角磨盤親撥
<lb ed="X" n="0304b09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b01"/>轉。無限樹子倚雲栽。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示馬文先居士</cb:mulu><head>示馬文先居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304b1101">話頭一句如弦直。不是牛兮不是驢。蹄角皮毛消得
<lb ed="X" n="0304b12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b04"/>盡。灼然露出頂門珠。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示何允量居士</cb:mulu><head>示何允量居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304b1401">話頭一句如弦直。跛脚猫兒睡正鼾。夜半經行誰共
<lb ed="X" n="0304b15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b07"/>語。月光花影恣清談。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示姚鄰卿居士</cb:mulu><head>示姚鄰卿居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304b1701">話頭一句如弦直。進步寧知行路難。稍得順風催客
<lb ed="X" n="0304b18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b10"/>便。蕭然無意過三灘。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示陳非白居士</cb:mulu><head>示陳非白居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304b2001">話頭一句如弦直。入處應從侍者邊。定動更知將智
<lb ed="X" n="0304b21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b13"/><g ref="#CB15072">󳫠</g>。門庭高峻古今傳。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示范爾培居士</cb:mulu><head>示范爾培居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304b23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304b2301">話頭一句如弦直。急水灘中下足難。行過夜明宮殿
<lb ed="X" n="0304b24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b16"/>裏。嚴霜六月透心寒。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0304c" n="0304c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示鄧直卿居士</cb:mulu><head>示鄧直卿居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0241b18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304c0201">話頭一句如弦直。水底游魚樹上鵶。眉下頓開清白
<lb ed="X" n="0304c03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a01"/>眼。笑看塵境亂如麻。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示余未也居士</cb:mulu><head>示余未也居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304c0501">話頭一句如弦直。鳥道羊腸路可行。行到水窮山盡
<lb ed="X" n="0304c06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a04"/>處。廓然天地是同庚。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示齊羣玉太守</cb:mulu><head>示齊羣玉太守</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304c0801">話頭一句如弦直。寶網香雲眼裏花。透過氷山并雪
<lb ed="X" n="0304c09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a07"/>洞。相逢且喫趙州茶。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示方時生貢元</cb:mulu><head>示方時生貢元</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304c1101">話頭一句如弦直。似吼春雷起蟄龍。情解那容些子
<lb ed="X" n="0304c12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a10"/>在。善行須信轍無蹤。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示姚純甫貢元</cb:mulu><head>示姚純甫貢元</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304c1401">話頭一句如弦直。機發靈樞應不窮。知是自家真現
<lb ed="X" n="0304c15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a13"/>量。四方八面起清風。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示張述之貢元</cb:mulu><head>示張述之貢元</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304c1701">話頭一句如弦直。凡聖量情不礙膺。獨蹈大方何境
<lb ed="X" n="0304c18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a16"/>界。倒騎鐵馬向空行。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示齊理侯居士</cb:mulu><head>示齊理侯居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242a18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304c2001">話頭一句如弦直。業識消磨六月霜。煩惱叢中開眼
<lb ed="X" n="0304c21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b01"/>看。皮囊盡放紫金光。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示齊季籲居士</cb:mulu><head>示齊季籲居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0304c23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0304c2301">話頭一句如弦直。生逼魚蛇化活龍。大地山河成粉
<lb ed="X" n="0304c24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b04"/>末。眉毛血濺梵天紅。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0305a" n="0305a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示胡康生居士</cb:mulu><head>示胡康生居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305a0201">話頭一句如弦直。捷疾雄奔木馬嘶。萬壑千峯都蹋
<lb ed="X" n="0305a03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b07"/>遍。珊瑚枝上摘摩尼。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示胡凝生居士</cb:mulu><head>示胡凝生居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305a0501">話頭一句如弦直。祖令全提向上玄。不向意言生卜
<lb ed="X" n="0305a06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b10"/>度。路頭筆直到家園。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示方奕予居士</cb:mulu><head>示方奕予居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305a0801">話頭一句如弦直。人在氷山雪洞來。時節不同塵世
<lb ed="X" n="0305a09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b13"/>界。桃花九月滿園開。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示戴式其居士</cb:mulu><head>示戴式其居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305a1101">話頭一句如弦直。栢子庭前語最親。略彴橋邊行下
<lb ed="X" n="0305a12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b16"/>過。通人那肯問關津。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示盛集陶居士</cb:mulu><head>示盛集陶居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0242b18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305a1401">話頭一句如弦直。瓶瀉雲興也是閒。佛法若從知解
<lb ed="X" n="0305a15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a01"/>入。少林端不把心安。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示姚申甫居士</cb:mulu><head>示姚申甫居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305a1701">話頭一句如弦直。混入方知不夜天。路載碧雲雲載
<lb ed="X" n="0305a18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a04"/>月。無身人坐案山前。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示劉胤平狀元</cb:mulu><head>示劉胤平狀元</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305a2001">話頭一句如弦直。飯後頻斟趙老茶。<g ref="#CB15081">䇿</g>杖喜隨流水
<lb ed="X" n="0305a21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a07"/>去。深林無伴看飛鴉。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示劉君含居士</cb:mulu><head>示劉君含居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305a23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305a2301">話頭一句如弦直。行遍三千及大千。掉轉身來何境
<lb ed="X" n="0305a24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a10"/>界。夜明簾外月當天。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0305b" n="0305b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示劉六合居士</cb:mulu><head>示劉六合居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305b0201">話頭一句如弦直。混入靈源不記年。識得自心元是
<lb ed="X" n="0305b03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a13"/>佛。更於何處覓金仙。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示劉爾敬居士</cb:mulu><head>示劉爾敬居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305b0501">話頭一句如弦直。梵語唐言義不殊。搬盡世間閒骨
<lb ed="X" n="0305b06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a16"/>董。清風明月滿庭除。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示劉爾靜居士</cb:mulu><head>示劉爾靜居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243a18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305b0801">話頭一句如弦直。水底紅塵山上魚。布袋都來收拾
<lb ed="X" n="0305b09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b01"/>盡。珊瑚枝上喜跏趺。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示洞如禪人</cb:mulu><head>示洞如禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305b1101">話頭一句如弦直。六月炎天火裏霜。須信目前無別
<lb ed="X" n="0305b12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b04"/>法。溪深杓柄自然長。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示微密禪人</cb:mulu><head>示微密禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305b1401">話頭一句如弦直。狹路相逢罷問程。脚下原無勾絞
<lb ed="X" n="0305b15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b07"/>索。橫牽直絆不須驚。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示慧林禪人</cb:mulu><head>示慧林禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305b1701">話頭一句如弦直。度盡眾生佛是魔。魔佛兩關都透
<lb ed="X" n="0305b18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b10"/>過。陽春白雪和巴歌。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示慈水禪人</cb:mulu><head>示慈水禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305b2001">話頭一句如弦直。夢醒忻看劫外春。遍野牛羊足水
<lb ed="X" n="0305b21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b13"/>草。莫教蹋破嶺頭雲。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示宗伯禪人</cb:mulu><head>示宗伯禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305b23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305b2301">話頭一句如弦直。開眼須知合眼時。明暗兩頭無著
<lb ed="X" n="0305b24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b16"/>處。倒吹鐵笛咏新詩。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0305c" n="0305c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示水澄禪人</cb:mulu><head>示水澄禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0243b18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305c0201">話頭一句如弦直。<g ref="#CB15081">䇿</g>杖尋溪得自由。撞著木人開口
<lb ed="X" n="0305c03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a01"/>問。無言笑指水東流。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示玄燦禪人</cb:mulu><head>示玄燦禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305c0501">話頭一句如弦直。喝水成氷當等閒。拄杖纔行三兩
<lb ed="X" n="0305c06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a04"/>步。幾多花雨落人間。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示云知禪人</cb:mulu><head>示云知禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305c0801">話頭一句如弦直。直入重樓最上層。公案萬千成粉
<lb ed="X" n="0305c09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a07"/>碎。阿誰敢曰續傳燈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示荊山禪人</cb:mulu><head>示荊山禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305c1101">話頭一句如弦直。喫飯穿衣最上乘。就裏不生分別
<lb ed="X" n="0305c12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a10"/>想。道人行處火消氷。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示中和禪人</cb:mulu><head>示中和禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305c1401">話頭一句如弦直。山自青兮水自藍。活計不從人處
<lb ed="X" n="0305c15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a13"/>得。清風明月是同參。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示道菴禪人</cb:mulu><head>示道菴禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305c1701">話頭一句如弦直。你既無心我也休。華藏莊嚴原具
<lb ed="X" n="0305c18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a16"/>足。貫珠寶網不他求。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示弘覬禪人</cb:mulu><head>示弘覬禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244a18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305c2001">話頭一句如弦直。誰是緣生誰是真。坐斷兩頭無點
<lb ed="X" n="0305c21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b01"/>事。庭前應笑看花人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示□□禪人</cb:mulu><head>示□□禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0305c23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0305c2301">話頭一句如弦直。世道紛紜作麼生。直入萬花叢裏
<lb ed="X" n="0305c24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b04"/>過。不沾些子始通身。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0306a" n="0306a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示寂常禪人</cb:mulu><head>示寂常禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306a0201">話頭一句如弦直。勿論他家短與長。生死岸頭何捷
<lb ed="X" n="0306a03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b07"/>徑。疑情粉碎罷商量。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示智華禪人</cb:mulu><head>示智華禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306a0501">話頭一句如弦直。無位真人倒著<g ref="#CB15595">󳳫</g>。行到水窮山盡
<lb ed="X" n="0306a06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b10"/>處。通身渾是佛陀耶。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示慧生禪人</cb:mulu><head>示慧生禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306a0801">話頭一句如弦直。討甚閒心鼓是非。迸破疑團清夢
<lb ed="X" n="0306a09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b13"/>裏。相逢難與話離微。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示湛之禪人</cb:mulu><head>示湛之禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306a1101">話頭一句如弦直。梅熟何勞更索核。吐盡口中酸澀
<lb ed="X" n="0306a12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b16"/>味。齒牙應有暗香來。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示小枝禪人</cb:mulu><head>示小枝禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0244b18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306a1401">話頭一句如弦直。幽谷芝蘭分外香。浪靜水平人不
<lb ed="X" n="0306a15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a01"/>語。鴛鴦鳧鳥自成行。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示小止禪人</cb:mulu><head>示小止禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306a1701">話頭一句如弦直。直下承當早是遲。父母未生前面
<lb ed="X" n="0306a18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a04"/>目。不勞開口貴先知。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示曹印禪人</cb:mulu><head>示曹印禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306a2001">話頭一句如弦直。佛是靈山老比丘。以手自家頭上
<lb ed="X" n="0306a21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a07"/>摸。不須螺髻也風流。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示玄京禪人</cb:mulu><head>示玄京禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306a23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306a2301">話頭一句如弦直。博得靈源活水長。分派不生高下
<lb ed="X" n="0306a24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a10"/>想。成渠何必細參詳。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0306b" n="0306b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示瑞雲禪人</cb:mulu><head>示瑞雲禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306b0201">話頭一句如弦直。勘破塵勞語最親。撿得乾柴烹活
<lb ed="X" n="0306b03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a13"/>水。自斟自酌不干人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示恒如禪人</cb:mulu><head>示恒如禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306b0501">話頭一句如弦直。風雨無停竟到家。却笑後園驢喫
<lb ed="X" n="0306b06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a16"/>草。夕陽西照影偏斜。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示葛皖伯居士</cb:mulu><head>示葛皖伯居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245a18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306b0801">話頭一句如弦直。雪夜安心不是心。好看當年干木
<lb ed="X" n="0306b09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b01"/>客。石頭路上水泥深。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示純素禪人</cb:mulu><head>示純素禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306b1101">話頭一句如弦直。水面燈毬火裏蓮。雪洞氷山穿下
<lb ed="X" n="0306b12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b04"/>過。長安盡處更加鞭。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示江達所居士</cb:mulu><head>示江達所居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b06"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306b1401">話頭一句如弦直。脚下黃泥知幾深。垢膩汗衫都脫
<lb ed="X" n="0306b15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b07"/>盡。從他撩亂不關心。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示許圓脩居士</cb:mulu><head>示許圓脩居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306b1701">話頭一句如弦直。日不勞兮夜不眠。自古鼻端無點
<lb ed="X" n="0306b18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b10"/>氣。何須特地慕腥羶。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示程君鑒居士</cb:mulu><head>示程君鑒居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b12"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306b2001">話頭一句如弦直。就路還家太鈍生。曠劫本無些變
<lb ed="X" n="0306b21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b13"/>易。何須特地越規行。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示芮含實居士</cb:mulu><head>示芮含實居士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306b23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306b2301">話頭一句如弦直。十八兒郎笑未休。撿得糞頭無價
<lb ed="X" n="0306b24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b16"/>寶。幾多歡喜幾多愁。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0306c" n="0306c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示覺海菴主</cb:mulu><head>示覺海菴主</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0245b18"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c0201">話頭一句如弦直。不落思量第二籌。推倒須彌穿屐
<lb ed="X" n="0306c03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a01"/>走。毗盧頂上滑如油。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示眾禪人</cb:mulu><head>示眾禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c0501">話頭一句如弦直。空裏浮雲鏡裏花。看罷莫生奇特
<lb ed="X" n="0306c06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a04"/>想。從來黑豆不生芽。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a05"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c0701">話頭一句如弦直。當下無心見本來。干木更須牢把
<lb ed="X" n="0306c08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a06"/>定。衡山路上滑如苔。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a07"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c0901">話頭一句如弦直。地覆天翻不動心。祇有一條生活
<lb ed="X" n="0306c10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a08"/>計。隨緣愈入愈知深。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c1101">話頭一句如弦直。無耳人聞說法聲。雲水盡時歌舞
<lb ed="X" n="0306c12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a10"/>罷。長安大道坦然平。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a11"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c1301">話頭一句如弦直。底事分明不許知。動著些兒遭藥
<lb ed="X" n="0306c14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a12"/>忌。離言誰肯辯深慈。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a13"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c1501">話頭一句如弦直。聞說何如見面親。縱是風恬閒不
<lb ed="X" n="0306c16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a14"/>徹。還憐活水躍金鱗。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a15"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c1701">一句話頭如鐵橛。碧雲深處有家傳。相逢不必重宣
<lb ed="X" n="0306c18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a16"/>說。處處春風楊柳天。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c19"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a17"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c1901">一句話頭如鐵橛。死中要箇活人來。六根粉碎成團
<lb ed="X" n="0306c20"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246a18"/>去。優鉢羅花遍界開。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c21"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b01"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c2101">一句話頭如鐵橛。縱橫萬境也教閒。脚跟不帶些泥
<lb ed="X" n="0306c22"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b02"/>水。收拾行囊過故山。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0306c23"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b03"/><p xml:id="pX72p0306c2301">一句話頭如鐵橛。三千里外步如初。從來心法無前
<lb ed="X" n="0306c24"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b04"/>境。大地收來一草廬。</p>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X72.1435.0307a" n="0307a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a01"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b05"/><p xml:id="pX72p0307a0101">一句話頭如鐵橛。動中消息是如何。纖毫不盡隨生
<lb ed="X" n="0307a02"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b06"/>滅。笑殺當年凌行婆。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a03"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b07"/><p xml:id="pX72p0307a0301">一句話頭如鐵橛。驪龍頷下抉珠時。只須不顧危亡
<lb ed="X" n="0307a04"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b08"/>也。入手方知出世奇。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a05"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b09"/><p xml:id="pX72p0307a0501">一句話頭如鐵橛。紛紜境界體如如。只消識取來時
<lb ed="X" n="0307a06"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b10"/>路。倒跨楊岐三脚驢。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a07"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b11"/><p xml:id="pX72p0307a0701">一句話頭如鐵橛。多年故紙不須鑽。一朝家當都拋
<lb ed="X" n="0307a08"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b12"/>却。始覺從前被眼瞞。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a09"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b13"/><p xml:id="pX72p0307a0901">一句話頭如鐵橛。眉毛動處即須知。衲僧氣宇天然
<lb ed="X" n="0307a10"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b14"/>大。莫只因循十二時。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a11"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示五葉侍者</cb:mulu><head>示五葉侍者</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a12"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b16"/><p xml:id="pX72p0307a1201">一句話頭如鐵橛。三玄五位不須論。千經萬典都拋
<lb ed="X" n="0307a13"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b17"/>却。掃地焚香是甚人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a14"/><lb ed="R125" n="0246b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示融愚禪人</cb:mulu><head>示融愚禪人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a15"/><lb ed="R125" n="0247a01"/><p xml:id="pX72p0307a1501">一句話頭如鐵橛。活中要箇死人來。相逢為報鄉關
<lb ed="X" n="0307a16"/><lb ed="R125" n="0247a02"/>事。紫莖金櫻帶露開。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a17"/><lb ed="R125" n="0247a03"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0307a18"/><lb ed="R125" n="0247a04"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="018"><cb:jhead>無異禪師廣錄卷第十八</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></body>
